title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table that contains a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row, an exception is thrown.
EB: The data should be exported successfully without any exceptions.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Add a table with a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 3. Preview the report. 4. Try to export the data from the table and observe the exception being thrown.
